OL,3,CNew law bans marriage behind bars for
OL,4,Cworst offenders
OL,6,FSerial killer Levi Bellfield has been
OL,7,Fblocked from having a civil
OL,8,Fpartnership, after a new law came into
OL,9,Fforce stopping the most serious
OL,10,Foffenders getting married behind bars.
OL,12,FBellfield is serving two whole life
OL,13,Forders for killing 13-year-old Milly
OL,14,FDowler, Marsha McDonnell and Amelie
OL,15,FDelagrange, as well as the attempted
OL,16,Fmurder of Kate Sheedy.
