OL,3,CNew law bans marriage behind bars for
OL,4,Cworst offenders
OL,6,FIt is understood he had recently
OL,7,Fsubmitted an application for a civil
OL,8,Fpartnership, which is believed to have
OL,9,Fspurred the Government on to bring the
OL,10,Fpreviously-announced restriction in
OL,11,Ffrom Friday.
OL,13,FPreviously Bellfield had applied to
OL,14,Fmarry his girlfriend and made a bid
OL,15,Ffor legal aid to challenge a decision
OL,16,Fto block his marriage.
