OL,3,CNew law bans marriage behind bars for
OL,4,Cworst offenders
OL,6,FIt was reported at the time by The Sun
OL,7,Fthat he had won a bid to be granted up
OL,8,Fto #30,000 in legal aid after his
OL,9,Flawyers cited the European Convention
OL,10,Fon Human Rights and the 1983 Marriage
OL,11,FAct.
OL,13,FIt is understood he withdrew his
OL,14,Fapplication to get married but had
OL,15,Fsubmitted a new application for a
OL,16,Fcivil partnership in recent months.
