OL,3,CNew law bans marriage behind bars for
OL,4,Cworst offenders
OL,6,FThe new law, which is part of the
OL,7,FVictims and Prisoners Act, aims to
OL,8,F"deny the most heinous criminals from
OL,9,Fenjoying the important life events
OL,10,Fthey callously took from their
OL,11,Fvictims", the Ministry of Justice
OL,12,F(MoJ) said.
OL,14,FIt applies to those serving whole life
OL,15,Forders.
OL,17,FPreviously such prisoners could make a
OL,18,Fformal application for marriage or a
OL,19,Fcivil partnership and could only be
OL,20,Frefused by a prison governor on the
OL,21,Fgrounds of security concerns.
