OL,3,CNew law bans marriage behind bars for
OL,4,Cworst offenders
OL,6,FLord Chancellor and Justice Secretary,
OL,7,FShabana Mahmood, said: "Victims should
OL,8,Fnot be tormented by seeing those who
OL,9,Fcommit the most depraved crimes enjoy
OL,10,Fthe moments in life that were stolen
OL,11,Ffrom their loved ones.
OL,13,F"That is why I have acted as soon as
OL,14,Fpossible to stop these marriages and
OL,15,Fgive victims the support they deserve."
OL,17,FThe Lord Chancellor will retain the
OL,18,Fright to permit ceremonies in the most
OL,19,Fexceptional circumstances, the MoJ
OL,20,Fsaid.
