OL,3,CNew law bans marriage behind bars for
OL,4,Cworst offenders
OL,6,FBellfield received a whole life
OL,7,Fsentence for the murder of Ms
OL,8,FMcDonnell, 19, in 2003, Ms Delagrange,
OL,9,F22, and the attempted murder of Ms
OL,10,FSheedy, 18, in 2004.
OL,12,FHe was already serving his sentence
OL,13,Fwhen he went on trial for killing
OL,14,Fschoolgirl Milly, who was snatched
OL,15,Ffrom the street walking home from
OL,16,Fschool in Walton-on-Thames, Surrey, in
OL,17,FMarch 2002.
OL,19,FHe was found guilty of abducting and
OL,20,Fkilling the 13-year-old following a
OL,21,Ftrial at the Old Bailey in 2011.
